# Salon-specific images directory
# 
# Structure:
# public/salons/cinderella/
# public/salons/glamstudio/
# public/salons/rosebeauty/
#
# Each salon directory can contain:
# - gallery1.jpg, gallery2.jpg, etc.
# - before1.jpg, after1.jpg (transformations)
# - hero.jpg (optional hero background)
#
# Images can be referenced in config as:
# {
#   "image": "/salons/cinderella/gallery1.jpg"
# }
#
# This structure enables storing salon-specific images
# while maintaining a single deployment.
